[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "硝烟散尽后，凯茜娅看到了正朝她走来的薇蒂雅和苔丝。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_girl015_01",
        "zh_CN": "你们要是再慢一些，就用不着动手了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_girl017_01",
        "zh_CN": "凯茜娅小姐，我们可没办法变成信息态呐。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_girl017_02",
        "zh_CN": "而且，你还是先缓口气吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "苔丝和薇蒂雅都能看出，凯茜娅显然有些体力不支。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "即使是凯茜娅，在空中连续使用信息态穿梭二十米以上的距离也是一件相当费力的事情。更何况，她还单枪匹马解决了数十台机兵。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "薇蒂雅天鹅座",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_girl018_01",
        "zh_CN": "这些机兵……是被埃达控制了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_girl015_02",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，不过反正它们也会阻止我们调查学院，在这里一锅端了也好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嘴上这么说着，凯茜娅的眼中却充满了怨气。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她本以为解决这些机兵花不了多少时间，结果最终还是放跑了埃达。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_girl015_03",
        "zh_CN": "没想到那家伙能够像playername一样使用泰坦物质进行防御。早知道应该用更保险一些的攻击方式……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说到这里，凯茜娅方才察觉到一件事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_girl015_04",
        "zh_CN": "等等，playername怎么没有和你们一起过来？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_girl017_03",
        "zh_CN": "分析员猜到了埃达可能会用各种方法阻止你，所以他让我们来帮你，而他自己走捷径去追埃达。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_girl015_05",
        "zh_CN": "两手准备，这倒的确是playername的作风。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "稍微放下些心后，凯茜娅看了看四周，又重新皱起了眉头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但在这地方，哪有分析员所说的捷径？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在建筑内，的确没有能快速接近埃达的捷径。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但我掌握着最为重要的东西，那便是情报。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那个曾待在我的意识空间内的意识体埃达，直到刚才，我都无法和它取得联系。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我事先预想到了埃达人间体会想办法切断我们之间的沟通，因此也没有寄希望于这件事情上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然而，在凯茜娅突袭埃达人间体的同时，我看到了意识体埃达出现在空中，凭空创造出了泰坦物质屏障。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "由于只有我才能看到那个意识体，因此在凯茜娅眼中，埃达人间体的防御完全是突然出现的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而我射出的那颗紧随其后的子弹击中了人间体，就在那个瞬间，我忽然察觉到，与埃达意识体之间的联系恢复了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "埃达？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我在心中如此默念了一句，随即便听到了如同近在耳边的回应。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "受缚的埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_sfaida_01",
        "zh_CN": "哎？分析员？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它似乎也没有预料到现在的情况。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "受缚的埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_sfaida_02",
        "zh_CN": "你先听我解释，我刚才不是故意要……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我知道，你只是想保住这具身体吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "受缚的埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_sfaida_03",
        "zh_CN": "哎嘿嘿，你能理解就太好了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "受缚的埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_sfaida_04",
        "zh_CN": "那么，你现在能感知到我的位置吗？我已经迫不及待想要见到你啦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可以，我很快就来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "受缚的埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_sfaida_05",
        "zh_CN": "好耶！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "意识体应答的同时，我却忽然听到了一阵吃痛的惨叫声。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你那边没问题吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "受缚的埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_sfaida_06",
        "zh_CN": "没事没事，有事的是她，不是我啦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这家伙，性格还是一如既往的糟糕啊。如果之后有机会的话，我需要管教一下它了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过现在，还是暂时把这些事情抛在脑后吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我深吸了一口气，透过层层建筑阻隔，正在逃走的埃达人间体的动向被我尽收眼底。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而我们之间最短的距离就是——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我大步奔跑起来，一口气冲出了建筑物内。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我的脚下，泰坦物质如树枝一般从窗口延伸而出，搭成了一座直通对面的桥梁。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只需要这样做，我到达埃达那里，连十秒都不需要。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达·人间体",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_snaida_01",
        "zh_CN": "只要能……只要能到达那个地方……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "埃达人间体确信自己已经逃脱了凯茜娅的追击。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "周围安静得可怕，除了自己的心跳、喘息与脚步声外，她完全听不到别的声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "现在，她离出口通道仅仅只有十米距离。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "三步、两步，近在咫尺……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在这时，出口忽然暗了下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一个人影挡住了从出口透进室内的光，而那正是埃达人间体此时此刻最不想见到的人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "受缚的埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_sfaida_07",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你来啦！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "到此为止了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达·人间体",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_snaida_02",
        "zh_CN": "呃！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就像是凭空挨了一拳，埃达人间体痛苦地捂住了自己的腹部。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "过于紧张导致的胃痛吗？呵，你的确已经是人类了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我慢慢走近，朝着人间体抬起了手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_aida_01",
        "zh_CN": "也许，成为一个人类是一个糟糕的决定。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在我准备进入埃达人间体的意识空间时，熟悉的声音凭空响起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在人间体的身旁，红色的埃达悄然出现在空中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_aida_02",
        "zh_CN": "去老地方聊聊吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它平静地宣布着自己的想法，下一刻，我便感觉到自己的意识被抽离了身体。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "瓦尔哈拉空间，我已经许久没有踏足这里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "相比上一次，我的精神力量已经有了巨大的提升，我能感觉到自己可以在一定程度上影响这里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_aida_03",
        "zh_CN": "欢迎回家，playername。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我和埃达相距很远，但在这样一个由意识主导的空间中，即使远在天涯海角，我也能清楚地听到它的声音，看清它的一举一动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我们之间，漂浮着一块巨大的方形投影。在它朝上的一面，赫然画着纵横十九道直线。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是一块围棋棋盘。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在没有电子设备的时代，这种历史悠久的棋类曾是人类重要的娱乐活动。在后成年病时代，则与许多其他的娱乐活动一样经历了不可避免的衰落。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_aida_04",
        "zh_CN": "自从上次与你交谈之后，我又思考了许多东西。所以，我决定用新的相处模式来面对你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep4_aida_05",
